certifications.title: Introduction to Frontend development with reactJs

projects.name: Hospital Appointment System
projects.description: Developed using Angular for frontend, NodeJS with ExpressJs for backend, and MySQL for database management. Designed and implemented a dynamic Hospital Appointment System. Users can book appointments and provide descriptions of their medical needs. Admins can manage appointments and doctors' lists. Features include user and admin logins, showcasing proficiency in full-stack development and efficient use of Angular and NodeJS for a seamless user experience.

projects.name: Movie-booking app
projects.description: Developed using Angular for frontend, NodeJS with ExpressJS for backend, and MySQL for database management. Created a user-friendly platform for booking movie tickets, providing details on movies, showtimes, and theaters. Users can securely book tickets and manage their bookings. Admin features enable efficient management of bookings, theaters, and movie listings.

projects.name: VaxEase
projects.description: Developed using Angular, Flask, and SQLite, VaxEase powers a robust and efficient COVID vaccine appointment system, essential in navigating the challenges posed by the pandemic. VaxEase revolutionizes vaccination scheduling with a seamless, secure platform for users, ensuring confidence in appointment booking for their vaccines. Administrators efficiently manage centers, schedules, and contribute to the broader vaccination effort.

projects.name: Food - Recipe website
projects.description: Developed using Angular for frontend, NodeJS with ExpressJs for backend and MYSQL for database management. Designed and implemented a dynamic Food Website. Users can explore recipes, access detailed instructions, and use search functionality. Features include a 'Favorites' option for saving preferred recipes, showcasing proficiency in front-end development and Angular framework for an engaging user experience.

experiences.description: Completed a virtual internship through IBM SkillsBuild, acquiring practical knowledge in frontend development technologies including HTML,CSS and JavaScript. Gained valuable hands-on experience during the internship, actively developing and implementing frontend technologies under the guidance of industry professionals.
